description.p:
The alloys as steel stocks for the Fe-Ni alloy pipe stocks of the prevent invention can selectively contain, in addition to the above-mentioned components, one or more of elements of each group described below as occasion demands:
(i) One or more elements selected from among V: 0.001 to 0.3%, Nb: 0.001 to 0.3%, Ta: 0.001 to 1.0%, Ti: 0.001 to 1.0%, Zr: 0.001 to 1.0% and Hf: 0.001 to 1.0%;
(ii) B: 0.0001 to 0.015%;
(iii) Co: 0.3 to 5.0%; and
(iv) One or more elements selected from among Mg: 0.0001 to 0.010%, Ca: 0.0001 to 0.010%, La: 0.0001 to 0.20%, Ce: 0.0001 to 0.20%, Y: 0.0001 to 0.40%, Sm: 0.0001 to 0.40%, Pr: 0.0001 to 0.40% and Nd: 0.0001 to 0.50%. That is to say, one or more elements of the four groups (i) to (iv) can be added thereto as optional additive elements.
